answers.answer: Anyone else have preeclampsia? What are/were your symptoms?
I have to do the same thing ... They want to check me for preeclamsia . Symptoms are high blood pressure protein in urine sudden weight gain ,swelling ,headaches , nausea ,change in vision ect.

question: I am 37w 2 days due the 28th and apparently there is protein in my urine... now I'm doing the 24 hour urine collection. My bp has steadily been rising but is only elevated slightly and not high. They are talking about inducing me thursday too... for some reason I get the feeling they are doing it just to induce me so I don't have the baby on Christmas because I don't have symptoms of preeclampsia besides them telling me I have protein.
title: 24 hour urine collection & induction?
